name: HireRight
description: HireRight is a leading provider of on-demand employment background checks, drug testing, Form I-9 and employment and education verifications.

configuration.name: Endpoint URL
configuration.description: The URL for the HireRight API.

configuration.name: Allow Select Fields parameter
configuration.description: Enables use of global fields query parameter to filter response to only specified fields. This will override any existing vendor functionality on the connector

configuration.name: WSDL Location
configuration.description: The wsdl url for your HireRight environment.

configuration.name: HireRight User Name
configuration.description: The user name for your HireRight account.

configuration.name: HireRight Password
configuration.description: The Password for your HireRight account.

configuration.name: HireRight Account Id
configuration.description: The account id for your HireRight account.

configuration.name: HireRight Company Login
configuration.description: The company login for your HireRight account.

configuration.name: HireRight User Ref Id
configuration.description: The User Ref Id for your HireRight account.

configuration.name: Event Notification Callback URL
configuration.description: An application callback URL used for event notifications from HireRight and Cloud Elements

configuration.name: Callback Notification Signature Key
configuration.description: A key used to generate a validation hash header of the event/bulk notification webhook callback payload

configuration.name: Filter null values from the response
configuration.description: Used to enable/disable filtering of null values from the responses.

configuration.name: Default select fields
configuration.description: Generic map used to specify default fields for bulk download and GET /all requests. Each key should be the canonical objectName and values may be specified as a comma-delimited string or a list of strings
